titleNullable: Apples: Monthly Prices in Five Cities
subtitleNullable: Monthly price of 1 kg of apples in Russian cities
descriptionNullable:
DISCLAIMER: not Apple the company, just apples the fruits!

This dataset contains monthly apple price observations. It comes from the Russian Statistical Service and will be updated whenever possible.

## Potential questions

There are many interesting things to consider:

1.  Seasonal analysis and forecast of the price
2. Using data from multiple regions to improve the model for one specific region
3. Exploration of seasonal variation
4. Some geoeconomical interpretation and visualisation of data
